    "text": "COVID Testing Transparency Act of 2020\n\nThis bill requires the Department of Health and Human Services (HHS) to publicly report, within 14 days, information about the results of COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) tests that HHS receives from laboratories. HHS must\u00a0update the information daily thereafter."
